just make your life way easier by eliminating a bunch of boilerplate code.\r\n\r\nTake the following code for example (excerpted from `main.py`).\r\n\r\n```python\r\n    parser.add_argument('--face', type=str, default='false', help='Face search mode')\r\n    # ...\r\n    _face = False if str(args.face).lower() == 'false' else True\r\n```\r\n\r\nWith Click, the code above can be replaced with:\r\n\r\n```python\r\n@click.option('--face', type=bool, default=True, help='Face search mode.')\r\n```","closed_by":{"login":"YoongiKim","id":38288705,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM4Mjg4NzA1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38288705?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim","html_url":"https://github.com/YoongiKim","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/YoongiKim/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/YoongiKim/AutoCrawler/issues/6/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/YoongiKim/AutoCrawler/issues/6/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}